com.virginmoneygiving.connect.sdk.v1.beans.fundraiser.response
Class AccessTokenDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.virginmoneygiving.connect.sdk.v1.beans.fundraiser.response.AccessTokenDetails

public class AccessTokenDetails
extends java.lang.Object

Contains the details of a valid access token after the authorisation code has been successfully exchanged via POST API call, or if the call fails, the error code and details.
